'''Beowulf Launch Party''' was an online event dated of [[24 May]] [[2014]] to celebrate the release of the book ''[[Beowulf: A Translation and Commentary]]''. It was organized by [[The Tolkien Society]] and [[Middle-earth Network]] with support from [[Tolkien Brasil]] and [[The Tolkienist]].
